snippet.title: Headlines from the Deep - A PS1-style adventure game about a fish-based media production!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://menacingmecha.itch.io/headlines-from-the-deep?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt There once was a diver, out at sea...

In a harsh storm one night, they became detached from their boat

Mistaken for a fish, they're taken to the offices of Coral News...

➡️ More from Callum https://menacingmecha.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
